  <!-- EN: Poison shuttle【Second-rate】 -->
  <RI_Weapon_DESword.label>毒心梭【二品】</RI_Weapon_DESword.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Second-rate】Melee weapon\n\nA shuttle that can fly freely, with a strong poison, is a terrible assassination weapon. -->
  <RI_Weapon_DESword.description>【二品】近战兵器\n\n一柄可以自由操控飞行的飞梭，以猛毒萃成，是一种可怕的暗杀武器。</RI_Weapon_DESword.description>
  <!-- EN: 剧毒飞刃 -->
  <RI_Weapon_DESword.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>剧毒飞梭</RI_Weapon_DESword.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>
