  <!-- EN: Jumen axe【Second-rate】 -->
  <RI_Weapon_JumenAxe.label>巨门斧【二品】</RI_Weapon_JumenAxe.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Second-rate】Melee weapon\n\nAn axe of ancient god soldiers, forged from a large amount of metal, it is carved all over the grain. When holding the axe to stimulate the aura, the axe will emit waves of low chirping, affecting the area of people. -->
  <RI_Weapon_JumenAxe.description>【二品】近战兵器\n\n一柄源自古代的神兵之斧，以大量的金属锻造而成，其上刻满了纹路。手持斧子的时候激发灵气，斧子会发出一阵阵低沉的鸣叫，影响范围内的人。</RI_Weapon_JumenAxe.description>
  <!-- EN: 破阵斧鸣 -->
  <RI_Weapon_JumenAxe.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>破阵斧鸣</RI_Weapon_JumenAxe.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
  <RI_Weapon_JumenAxe.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.cooldownGerund>冷却中</RI_Weapon_JumenAxe.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.cooldownGerund>
  <!-- EN: 斧刃 -->
  <RI_Weapon_JumenAxe.tools.0.label>斧刃</RI_Weapon_JumenAxe.tools.0.label>
  <!-- EN: 斧刃 -->
  <RI_Weapon_JumenAxe.tools.1.label>斧刃</RI_Weapon_JumenAxe.tools.1.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Rat whisker sword【Second-rate】 -->
  <RI_Weapon_RatWhiskerSword.label>鼠须剑【二品】</RI_Weapon_RatWhiskerSword.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Second-rate】Melee weapon\n\nA thin sword, because it is as small as a mouse's whiskers, so it is called a ratwhisker sword. -->
  <RI_Weapon_RatWhiskerSword.description>【二品】近战兵器\n\n一柄细剑，因为形似老鼠的胡须一般小巧，所以被称为鼠须剑。</RI_Weapon_RatWhiskerSword.description>
  <!-- EN: 势如破竹 -->
  <RI_Weapon_RatWhiskerSword.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>势如破竹</RI_Weapon_RatWhiskerSword.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
