  <!-- EN: 剑尖 -->
  <RI_Weapon_RatWhiskerSword.tools.1.label>剑尖</RI_Weapon_RatWhiskerSword.tools.1.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Thunder lord lance【Second-rate】 -->
  <RI_Weapon_ThunderLordLance.label>雷王枪【二品】</RI_Weapon_ThunderLordLance.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Second-rate】Melee weapon\n\nA long, powerful lance that sent lightning bolts all over its body. The weapon is said to have been as powerful as the First-rate weapon, but since it became too unstable, it has been modified to be less powerful and more controllable. -->
  <RI_Weapon_ThunderLordLance.description>【二品】近战兵器\n\n一柄威力强大的长枪，周身释放出道道闪电。这把武器据说曾是可以比肩一品的强大兵器，但之后由于过于不稳定，被经过改造，减小了威力，也更好控制了。</RI_Weapon_ThunderLordLance.description>
  <!-- EN: 卿云迅雷 -->
  <RI_Weapon_ThunderLordLance.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>卿云迅雷</RI_Weapon_ThunderLordLance.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
  <RI_Weapon_ThunderLordLance.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.cooldownGerund>冷却中</RI_Weapon_ThunderLordLance.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.cooldownGerund>
  <!-- EN: 枪头 -->
  <RI_Weapon_ThunderLordLance.tools.0.label>枪头</RI_Weapon_ThunderLordLance.tools.0.label>
  <!-- EN: 枪杆 -->
  <RI_Weapon_ThunderLordLance.tools.1.label>枪杆</RI_Weapon_ThunderLordLance.tools.1.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Wind demon blade【Second-rate】 -->
  <RI_Weapons_WindDemonBlade.label>风魔刀【二品】</RI_Weapons_WindDemonBlade.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Second-rate】Melee weapon\n\nA big blade to unleash the wind. Although it is made of metal, the veins on it are like blood vessels and tendons, and they throb faintly when waved. -->
  <RI_Weapons_WindDemonBlade.description>【二品】近战兵器\n\n一柄可以释放狂风的大刀。虽然是金属打造，但其上的纹路仿佛血管和肌腱一般，在挥动时隐隐跳动着。</RI_Weapons_WindDemonBlade.description>
  <!-- EN: 地煞狂风 -->
